headline: Rare Earth Boom: Defense Heavyweight Joins Critical Mineral Effort
summary: REalloys Inc. appoints GM Defense president Stephen S. duMont as non-executive chairman to align commercial growth with allied defense modernization and secure critical mineral supply chains.

headline: Option Volatility And Earnings Report For October 20 - 24
summary: It’s a big week of earnings with some big tech stocks and industrials due to report. This week we have Tesla, Netflix, Intel, Ford, Coca-Cola, International Business Machines, Freeport McMoran and Nemont Mining all reporting.
